Class ReportCriteria

java.lang.Object
Report.ReportCriteria
public class ReportCriteria extends Object
Represents a set of filtering criteria used for generating BTO project application reports. Criteria include marital status, flat type, age range, and neighborhood.

    • ReportCriteria

      public ReportCriteria(MaritalStatus maritalStatus, String flatType, Integer minAge, Integer maxAge, String neighborhood)
      Constructs a ReportCriteria with the specified values.
      Parameters:
      maritalStatus - the marital status to filter by (e.g., SINGLE or MARRIED)
      flatType - the flat type to filter by (e.g., "2-Room", "3-Room")
      minAge - the minimum age for filtering applicants
      maxAge - the maximum age for filtering applicants
      neighborhood - the neighborhood to filter projects by
